data.description: Welcome to Emerald Falls! Amazing newer construction with all of the upgrades! This home backs to a vast greenbelt with perfect views of the fishing pond. This home boasts a stunning granite island that seats 6 comfortably with plenty of counter space and cabinetry, stainless steel appliances which is open to the large dining area and huge family room with custom gas fireplace. Primary bedroom has ensuite bath with all of the amenities and walk in closet. Two good sized bedrooms share a full bath and then also a powder bath for guests. While sitting on the back patio and enjoy drinks, you can enjoy the views of the yard, green space and pond. Located just outside the city, but near everything you need!
